data.description: Views, Views, Views!!! This lovely home is nestled close to the mountains on an acre of land with NO HOA! Bring your RV or your horses and enjoy life in the country just a few minutes from town. Entertain on the beautiful 10X27 back deck or enjoy the ambiance of the backlit lighting from the gorgeous granite decorative wall in the living room. The large Master Suite boasts a walk-in closet, cathedral ceiling, double sinks, a luxurious garden tub with a separate shower and plenty of cabinets for storage. The kitchen is a chef's delight with newer appliances and plenty of storage. To complete the package there is a 16x18 detached shed, a tankless water heater, a metal carport, an owned propane tank and the electrical system has been upgraded to a 200 Amp panel and beautiful new flooring!
